lla","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/18257861/","username":"anonymous-d014490e77c0d8e5769e696fe439b676"},"score":1,"reply":null,"version":{"id":2372658,"version":"1.0"}},{"id":2025327,"addon":{"id":960423,"slug":"imakeclick","name":{"en-US":"autoClick"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/static-server/img/addon-icons/default-64.png"},"body":"Not sure why this has a bunch of one star review, it works just fine for my purposes (Cookie Clicker). Though there are a couple of things that prevent me from rating this add-on five stars. \n\nMy biggest issue with this is the lack of an option to increase the amount of clicks per second. If this is possible, it would make this add-on immensely better. \n\nMy other issue with this add-on is not having hotkeys to disable or enable it. As others have pointed out, being able to disable the add-on would prevent accidents on other sites. For me it's not too important since I can just go into the add-ons manager and disable it from there. However, including this feature would be of great convenience. \n\nOther than those two issues, this is a fine add-on which serves the purpose for any idle clicker games. I cannot understand the one star reviews for this add-on, perhaps there was some issue at the time others reviewed it but I have not encountered it. There are probably better programs, or hardware, out there, but for my situation it does what it's supposed to and does it nicely.","created":"2023-12-08T23:07:34Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":false,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":18186497,"name":"EmanLaerton","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/18186497/","username":"anonymous-8c1ba32044f46f776af7987a333ca8a4"},"score":3,"reply":null,"version":{"id":2372658,"version":"1.0"}},{"id":1986317,"addon":{"id":960423,"slug":"imakeclick","name":{"en-US":"autoClick"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/static-server/img/addon-icons/default-64.png"},"body":null,"created":